songs.title: Selfish (Demo)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Oooh, yeah

[Verse]
It was right
Even though it felt wrong
Nothin' ever stopped you
From showin' your progression suddenly

[Bridge]
Broken lies
Driving backwards
Making all the wrong turns
Saying all the wrong words
Dodging angels

[Pre-Chorus]
Oh, let's not be alone
Let's not be alone
Let's not be alone
Let's be one
Oh, let's not be alone

Empty thoughts fill the room
Breathe for me and I'll breathe for you

[Chorus]
Let's be selfish, 'fish
Tonight, tonight
Let's be selfish, 'fish
Tonight, tonight
Yeah, yeah
Let's be selfish, 'fish
Tonight, tonight
Let's be selfish
